cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper discusses Natural Language Processing (NLP) and evaluation of taxonomy learning approaches, which are commonly studied in the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses hypernymy detection, which is a task related to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The evaluation procedures mentioned in the paper are related to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and the proposed future work involves resources and downstream applications, which are related to Cybernetics (cs.CY).
